User Statements

As an application user I am able to check in a vehicle

As an application user I am able to enter the customer name

As an application user I am able to assign a license plate number (6 Digits)

As an application user I am able to input the Make of the car

As an application user I am able to input the model of the car

As an application user I am able to input the year of the car

As an application I am able to input color of the car

As an application user I am able to assign the vehicle a parking spot number

As an application user I am able to check out a car

As an application user I am able to view parking spots to see which are occupied

As an application user I am able to view the parking spots to see which are not occupied

As an application user I am able to calculate the cost of the parking time

As an application user I am able to assess whether or not the vehicle is an overnight stay

As an application user I am able to generate an Invoice for the customer

As an application user I am able to save the data to logs